    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once done, transfer the <strong>cooked chicken </strong>to a clean board and shred it apart, using two forks – this technique is known as ‘pulling’</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1688120579948-x200.jpg",
