            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1688120583513-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> chicken & tomato tortiglioni </strong>topped with the <strong>remaining grated Italian hard cheese</strong> and the<strong> spicy lemon garlic drizzle</strong></p><p><strong><span class=\"text-danger\">Tip: Cooking for kids? Leave out the spicy lemon garlic drizzle and just sprinkle over some grated cheese!</span></strong></p><p>Garnish with a <strong>lemon wedge </strong>and taste for seasoning, adding more <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> if needed</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
